{"tid":336024,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民族黨陳浩天當初錯判形勢，走去食陳根記，點解到宜家都無回應過？","createTime":"2017-07-26T05:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T12:12:43.000Z","uid":33481,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe380bd3ba8e8548d60806de7300c8da7a4bd30","tid":336024,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:35:56.000Z","msg":"連認錯都唔敢既垃圾組織，本質上同熱狗無分別，唔死都無用"},{"pid":"27509407b97651fee393d95f40eefbccac730471","tid":336024,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c2747080d364177d7fdb435b156a857a7df50c","tid":336024,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"有咩好回應<br />\n牙清泉邊敢得罪人"},{"pid":"f60fbed1c6722cac8cb072641eafdab035eda8db","tid":336024,"uid":62929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:22:37.000Z","msg":"陳根記正呀！"},{"pid":"258de846006e93333e1e8619492d2a54ef7a1ece","tid":336024,"uid":62929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"御理引述清泉天話民族黨個套公民民主義會害死香港<br />\n<br />\n清泉天就係之前個拍烏蠅學界論壇讚民族論 假到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939615144124f6b59e9372f9c97ad3d312763ced","tid":336024,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:51:05.000Z","msg":"食熱狗可以解做落熱狗面，咁食陳根記代表落陳雲面都好合理"},{"pid":"92dce2c4bec8474fb2369451f1826f9388d04573","tid":336024,"uid":45285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食熱狗可以解做落熱狗面，咁食陳根記代表落陳雲面都好合理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢隻熱狗成日都唔記得自己個組織領導人講乜&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  熱狗質素就係越來越差！<br />\n<br />\n黃洋達話食熱狗係撐熱狗，咁你呢隻熱狗覺得食陳根記係撐陳雲定落陳雲面呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004b7508a2c4e9dc0fb26205b6971526b57365cd","tid":336024,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩好回應<br />\n牙清泉邊敢得罪人</blockquote><br />\n清泉得罪過好多人，係唔敢得罪網上紅衛兵"},{"pid":"b75717ebbc12c347cab67122bfe778bb95e7648e","tid":336024,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"食陳根記有咩錯?"},{"pid":"ec3b4e7bd4e81462856036a6ad7aae4fdc70e19a","tid":336024,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食陳根記有咩錯?</blockquote><br />\n堡主天哥點會有錯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd801e45a46583b5482c6a9c692a3a202f72f981","tid":336024,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食陳根記有咩錯?</blockquote><br />\n堡主天哥點會有錯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你精神分裂呀? 一時話人唔認錯，一時又話人冇錯?"},{"pid":"d5888ee67d355f3dad914c14972ee8f2145c0648","tid":336024,"uid":33481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食陳根記有咩錯?</blockquote><br />\n堡主天哥點會有錯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你精神分裂呀? 一時話人唔認錯，一時又話人冇錯?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 民族黨智商...."},{"pid":"02cf2571d3d27c7c1ba548e3b1d18160be800bd9","tid":336024,"uid":34867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食熱狗可以解做落熱狗面，咁食陳根記代表落陳雲面都好合理</blockquote><br />\nhow about 網上食熱狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a98681ea2c89dd4c7b81a6d4937273424a1a23","tid":336024,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e001140ad1af0eea67625c611548b6b